{"root":{"data":{"id":"djmsnbljwao0","created":1782864298058,"text":"SOP相关"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmue5d33yg0","created":1782869221428,"text":"备注（Remarks）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-52.99999842047674,"y":159.99999523162865}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmuh4q0s5s0","created":1782869455125,"text":"lk抬头里面的\n  也是-MK的Remarks备注","layout_right_offset":{"x":63.999998092651424,"y":-27.999999165534973},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmufgl0h7c0","created":1782869324216,"text":"确保部件开料平整，没有粗糙。否则，油第⼀次粘合剂或底油前需要打磨或打砂，以使部件表⾯平整光滑。","layout_right_offset":{"x":5.750011395662511,"y":-34.24999940767901}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwsnrfowo0","created":1782876000795,"text":"Make sure the base of component is well prepared, that is not rough but neat. Otherwise, buffing or sanding is needed to make it flat and smooth before 1st promoter or 1st primer."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmujd80v6g0","created":1782869630357,"text":"所有部位及物料上必须使用粘合剂。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwv8mzce00","created":1782876202967,"text":"Promoter is needed to apply on all parts, all materials."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmujneny400","created":1782869652526,"text":"所有油好边油的部件需要至少自然干2至3小时，才可进行下一个生产工序。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwwkwn8gw0","created":1782876308037,"text":"All components finished with edge paint should be left to natural dry for at least 2 to 3 hours before proceeding to the next production stage."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmuk63ehg80","created":1782869693204,"text":"完成油边后，如果成品在正常天气条件下（~25-35℃，RH~60-70％）晾干，建议在24-48小时后进行包装。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwx0owgq80","created":1782876342397,"text":"After all edge painting process, under normal weather condition (~25-35℃, RH~60-70%), packaging is recommended to be proceeded after 24-48 hours. "},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmut52bl800","created":1782870396239,"text":"所有边油测试建议应在涂好边油后48小时后才进行，因为所有化工品都需要时间去作固化。尽管烘干机表面好像干了，但实则未干透固化，所以建议最好在48小时后才作包装或测试。","layout_right_offset":{"x":-4.249985191971405,"y":36.24999837949875}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwzumjm940","created":1782876564286,"text":"All tests of Edge paint are recommended to be proceeded after 48 hours, since edge paint needs time to be dried, cross-linked and fixed. Even with the use of drying machine to dry the edge paint, it is still not enough, as the paint is only dried superficially."},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmuujp3mk00","created":1782870506456,"text":"平边工艺（P2026060005）","layout_right_offset":{"x":20.74999910220498,"y":113.4999975487591}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmv15qclkw0","created":1782871024605,"text":"打磨操作时，材料应握紧且平直；打磨材料时应保持稳定且均匀的手势","layout_right_offset":{"x":16.50000189989794,"y":-12.499999441206398}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvfe9zcq80","created":1782872140305,"text":"During the buffing operation, the material should be held firmly and straight; the gesture used to buff the material should be steady and uniform."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv1vbucpc0","created":1782871080325,"text":"为呈现出最佳效果，最后一次打平边时需将物料朝同一方向打2 ~ 3次；","layout_right_offset":{"x":26.249998826533556,"y":-3.7499998323619934}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvg4p376o0","created":1782872197815,"text":"For optimal results, when buffing the edges for the last time, the material should be buffed in the same direction for 2 to 3 times."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv25ucprk0","created":1782871103212,"text":"由于弯角、转角圆形位置不易打磨，所以那些位置无法达到平边效果；","layout_right_offset":{"x":28.749998714774847,"y":1.2499999441205887}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvgglu5ns0","created":1782872223740,"text":"Due to the difficulty in buffing the rounded positions of bends and corners, it is impossible to achieve a flat edge effect at those locations."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv2p9pdgg0","created":1782871145499,"text":"根据不同的物料及厚度，调整油边的次数；","layout_right_offset":{"x":33.74999849125766,"y":-1.7053025658242404e-13}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvh81qq4o0","created":1782872283474,"text":"It is recommended to adjust the number of coats according to the absorption and the thickness of different material."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv2yfjmhc0","created":1782871165443,"text":"油边前需确保部件开料平整及贴合良好，没有胶水或杂质残留在皮边上。否则，油边前需要打磨或打砂，以使部件表面平整光滑；","layout_right_offset":{"x":32.499998547136784,"y":3.7499998323619366}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvhwidvko0","created":1782872336724,"text":"The material edges have to be clean, smooth and well compacted. Make sure the base of component is well cut, no glue or impurities remain on the edge of the material. Otherwise, buffing or sanding is needed to make it flat and smooth before edge paint application.","layout_right_offset":{"x":9.250102131311905,"y":4.583333294010856}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv4t4ymbk0","created":1782871310647,"text":"打平边效果前需要干燥6小时以上再进行打磨；","layout_right_offset":{"x":34.99999843537819,"y":12.499999441206455}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvnhevh0g0","created":1782872774044,"text":"Before achieving the desired edge effect, it is necessary to dry for at least 6 hours before buffing."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv9xmpgc80","created":1782871712248,"text":"平边效果对于边油的要求非常严格（粘度、消泡、饱满度、打磨性）；","layout_right_offset":{"x":27.99999597668642,"y":27.499998770654315}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvo3gczsg0","created":1782872822024,"text":"This effect has very strict requirements for edge paint (viscosity, defoaming, fullness, and polishability).","layout_right_offset":{"x":-24.999998882413024,"y":-3.749999832362164}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmvprstxpc0","created":1782872953385,"text":"边油自身的注意事项","layout_right_offset":{"x":37.49999832361948,"y":267.49998804181877}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmw70e3vv40","created":1782874304276,"text":"MK-一般皮边油操作程序（PMK202601001）","layout_right_offset":{"x":18.74999916180974,"y":353.7499841861432}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmw72z216w0","created":1782874309896,"text":"对于厚度为 3mm 以上、吸收性强或纤维松散的部件，可能需要多上⼀层以上的底油/⾊油. 对于厚度为 1.5mm 以下的部件, 可以少上⼀次底油","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmw95vunfs0","created":1782874472961,"text":"For the component with thickness higher than 3mm, high absorption characteristic, loose fiber… one or more coat of primer/color edge paint before the first buffing may be necessary. For the component with thickness less than 1.5mm, 1 coat of primer may be reduced."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmweek5gfs0","created":1782874883666,"text":"上⾯的粘度指标是针对于⼀般情况下的参考标准，由于粘度受季节温度、压强的影响会发⽣变化，我司会根据实际情况（比如⼯⼚的使⽤环境温度）来适当进⾏调整，所以，如原产地与⼯⼚当地温差⽐较⼤，粘度的误差相对也会⽐较⼤。","layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":6.249999720603455}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwhf15tm00","created":1782875119787,"text":"The above viscosity standard is for general circumstances. Since the viscosity will change easily due to the influence of seasonal temperature and pressure, also we will make appropriate adjustments according to the actual situation (such as the ambient temperature in production lines), thus, if the temperature difference is large between area of origin and the factory, the deviation would be relatively larger."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmwlqhowc00","created":1782875458187,"text":"粘合促进剂"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwlutff600","created":1782875467604,"text":"粘合促进剂的效能根据不同的物料会有差异，UA406H 能解决⼤部分但不是全部的脱边问题，所以强烈建议对应新做物料进⾏产前粘合测试，以保证⾜够的粘合⼒。如果粘合测试没达标，联络 D&A 以获得相应对策。","layout_right_offset":{"x":-5.249975357205358,"y":6.749999519437665}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwmlzm69s0","created":1782875526752,"text":"The ability of adhesion promoter depends on different type of material that UA406H generally solves most but not all of the peeling off issues, thus preliminary adhesion test on new material before production is strongly recommended to assure the adhesion ability. If it does not meet the standard, contact D&A for further action plans."},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmwpbuhjc00","created":1782875739766,"text":"（条件性）第二层色油"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwpkyd9940","created":1782875759592,"text":"在以下情况或需要再油一次或多次底油/边油：\na) 有些物料比较疏、松软、或吸收性强\nb) 部件厚度在3mm或以上","layout_right_offset":{"x":-3.9999998807907104,"y":17.99999946355797}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwr8k6ysg0","created":1782875889342,"text":"One or more coats of Primer / Color Edge Paint may be applied under following scenario:\na) the fiber of some materials/leather is too loose, empty, or absorptive.\nb) the thickness of the parts to be painted is 3mm or above"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmx29n96cg0","created":1782876753709,"text":"重要事项","layout_right_offset":{"x":15.999999523162955,"y":29.99999910593033}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmx2phgjtk0","created":1782876788187,"text":"油每层底油或边油的等候时间不要超过 4 ⼩时，因为过长的等候时间会影响层与层间的粘合⼒，引致脱落的风险很⾼。如果等候时间超过 4 ⼩时，油下⼀层底油或⾊油前需要先轻轻打磨⼀次。","layout_right_offset":{"x":164.00000232458103,"y":87.99999737739574}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmx3b0p9a00","created":1782876835063,"text":"The waiting time between applying coats of Primer and Edge paint onto the leather should NOT exceed 4 hours because long waiting time would affect the adhesion between coats that the risk of peeling off will be very high. If waiting time exceeds 4 hours, light buffing is necessary before applying new coats of primer or edge paint."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmx5jf95qw0","created":1782877010086,"text":"拉⼒测试机需要操作正常; 测试及计算⽅法需正确地按 MK 的要求进⾏。\n对于拉⼒测试套件，以下是设置的要求：\na) 顶部的称重传感器⽤于较厚的样品，例如⼿挽和肩带\nb) 第⼆个称重传感器⽤于较薄的样品，例如袋⾝和⽿仔。此称重传感器更灵敏，对较薄的样品给出更准确的结果\nc) 轴承上的垫圈有助于在拉起样品时保持黏着测试样的胶条不移动\nd) 胶条的厚度必须⼤于3.5mm","layout_right_offset":{"x":156.99998617172287,"y":183.99999451637336}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmx6xqpwm80","created":1782877119618,"text":"Peeling test machine should be in normal operation; testing methodology should be conducted properly according to MK requirement\nAs of peeling test kits, below is the requirement of the setting:\na) The 5kN Load Cell on top is used for Thicker Specimen e.g. handle and strap\nb) The 2nd 500N Load Cell is used for Thinner Specimen e.g. body and anchor. This Load Cell is more sensitive and gives more accurate result to\nthinner specimens\nc) Washers on bearing which helps to hold the acrylic with test specimen not to move while the specimen being pull up.\nd) While the acrylic must be 3.5mm> in thickness"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmxd53wn340","created":1782877605838,"text":"油下⼀次边油或打磨前，必须判断边油⾜够干透。由于干燥时间受天⽓条件和湿度的影响，所以干燥时间应适当调整以确保到边油⾜够干透。","layout_right_offset":{"x":161.999997586012,"y":241.999996393919}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmxd7yd5ts0","created":1782877612033,"text":"Edge paint must be confirmed to be dry enough before next application and buffing. Since drying time is affected by weather condition and humidity, therefore, drying time should be adjusted to when edge paint is dry enough. "},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djn0al93fo00","created":1782885869218,"text":"半透明金属色边油操作程序（P2019030004R2）","layout_right_offset":{"x":26.249999217689037,"y":832.2499752268202}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn0bi6jy800","created":1782885940898,"text":"根据不同的物料及客户的需求来决定是否用粘合剂。","layout_right_offset":{"x":18.749999441206455,"y":-104.99999687075638}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn0c0yp7vk0","created":1782885981782,"text":"Depending on material and customer requirement to decide applying adhesion promoter."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djn0cgx28v40","created":1782886016511,"text":"如有些物料比较吸油，饱满程度未能达到要求，则要再油一次底油或多次底油。","layout_right_offset":{"x":19.999999403953552,"y":-58.74999824911356}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn0cjg9yp40","created":1782886022027,"text":"Depending on absorption of material caused the covering do not meet requirement, then properly increase one or more coats of primer.","layout_right_offset":{"x":-7.499999776482355,"y":-7.499999776482582}},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmufnkb4co0","created":1782869339411,"text":"词语对照表","layout_mind_offset":{"x":493.999987125397,"y":-891.9999852776531}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmxmcetvj40","created":1782878327014,"text":"油轮","layout_right_offset":{"x":309.99999538064026,"y":-397.99999576807056}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn00gjqlzk0","created":1782885075336,"text":"D&A一号轮","layout_right_offset":{"x":215.4999972730875,"y":-23.4999996870755},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmxmjfl5wg0","created":1782878342297,"text":"D&A #1 roller","layout_right_offset":{"x":250.74999598413729,"y":-5.749999858438969}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn02dj6skw0","created":1782885225500,"text":"deep grooves roller","layout_right_offset":{"x":301.2499910220507,"y":-11.250003837048666}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djn00gjqlzk0","created":1782885075336,"text":"D&A二号轮","layout_right_offset":{"x":215.4999972730875,"y":-23.4999996870755},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmxmjfl5wg0","created":1782878342297,"text":"D&A #2 roller","layout_right_offset":{"x":250.74999598413729,"y":-10.749999709427357}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn02dj6skw0","created":1782885225500,"text":"medium grooves roller","layout_right_offset":{"x":323.74999035149847,"y":-7.500003948807375}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djn00gjqlzk0","created":1782885075336,"text":"D&A三号轮","layout_right_offset":{"x":215.4999972730875,"y":-23.4999996870755},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmxmjfl5wg0","created":1782878342297,"text":"D&A #3 roller","layout_right_offset":{"x":253.24999590963148,"y":-5.749999858438969}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn030f25i00","created":1782885275317,"text":"shallow grooves roller","layout_right_offset":{"x":324.99999031424534,"y":-14.999999552965164}},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djn03ij7ug00","created":1782885314750,"text":"油边例句","layout_right_offset":{"x":372.24998899549274,"y":-364.99998971819866}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn03ptu1eo0","created":1782885330630,"text":"用粗轮（参照 D&A 1 号轮）油第一次透明底油，待干透。","layout_right_offset":{"x":476.24998580664453,"y":-37.499998882413024}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn0426cu680","created":1782885357508,"text":"Apply 1st coat of colorless primer using deep grooves roller (refer to D&A #1 roller), let it dry. ","layout_right_offset":{"x":988.2499738857159,"y":-20.00000700354508}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djn06pjphxs0","created":1782885565110,"text":"用细轮（参照 D&A 3 号轮）油第一次高光边油（DMG 系列颜色），待自然干透。","layout_right_offset":{"x":607.4999781697993,"y":-28.74999914318323}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn07dw8pg00","created":1782885618110,"text":"Apply 1st coat of High Glossy Edge Paint (DMG series color) using fine grooves roller (refer to D&A #3 roller), let it dry naturally.","layout_right_offset":{"x":1293.7499522045264,"y":-14.250001005828608}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djn04x276mo0","created":1782885424737,"text":"打磨例句","layout_right_offset":{"x":371.49998898804216,"y":-131.2499947473409}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn052lrrmo0","created":1782885436804,"text":"用皮毡轮或羊毛轮打磨平滑, 用微湿毛巾擦干净。","layout_right_offset":{"x":426.24998729676054,"y":-22.49999932944786}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djn05chro340","created":1782885458330,"text":"Buff the surface by buffing machine with felt or wool wheel to make the surface smooth, clean by slightly wet towel.","layout_right_offset":{"x":1051.7499608471999,"y":-33.74999899417162}},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}